    <name>InnerBreeze</name>
    <summary>Meditate through breathing</summary> 
    <description>
        <p>InnerBreeze offers a unique meditation experience inspired by the Wim Hof Breathing method. Designed to promote relaxation, improve mental clarity, and enhance physical well-being, InnerBreeze guides users through a series of breathing exercises that help reduce stress, increase energy, and improve overall health.</p>
        <p>Whether you're a beginner or experienced in meditation, InnerBreeze provides a simple and effective way to incorporate breathing exercises into your daily routine, supporting a balanced mind and body.</p>
    </description>

